&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;General Matter has a massive body of critical-path engineering work ahead — nuclear licensing, integrated safety analysis, design criteria, technoeconomic&amp;nbsp;modeling. Conventional timelines for this work are too slow. We believe there is an opportunity to reinvent every single engineering workflow using modern AI.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
